-- France, U.K., Germany Say Terms of Bank Tax May Vary According to Country
-- Mark Deen
-- 2010-06-22T14:55:42Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-22/france-u-k-germany-say-terms-of-bank-tax-may-vary-according-to-country.html

          
          
             France, Germany and the U.K. may
vary the terms of new taxes on banks depending on their economic
situation and fiscal rules, the governments said in a joint
statement today.  
